---
---

<section class="section solution" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="container-wide">
    <div class="solution__layout">
      <div class="solution__visual reveal">
        <div class="solution__visual-main">
          <img
            src="/assets/imagery/moodboard.jpg"
            alt="Designer moodboard with materials, paint chips, and blueprints"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="solution__visual-accent">
          <img
            src="/assets/imagery/blueprint-contract.jpg"
            alt="Architectural blueprint and services agreement on a desk"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="solution__badge">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 2 4 6v6c0 5 3.5 9 8 10 4.5-1 8-5 8-10V6z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            <path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
          <div>
            <strong>No fluff. No upsells.</strong>
            <span>Just the playbook.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="solution__content reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--blue">YOUR NEW ADVANTAGE</span>
        <h2>Everything a pro knows.<br />Finally on your side of the table.</h2>
        <p class="solution__lead">
          Most remodel guides are written <em>for contractors</em>, by contractors.
          Get the Wolf is different. It's the only video course built <em>for you</em> —
          the homeowner who's about to hand a stranger $100,000 and a key to your house.
        </p>

        <ul class="solution__list">
          <li>
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" fill="var(--gtw-blue)" />
              <path d="m8 12 3 3 5-6" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <strong>50+ expert video lessons</strong>
              <span>Built for non-experts. No construction degree required.</span>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" fill="var(--gtw-blue)" />
              <path d="m8 12 3 3 5-6" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <strong>Printable scripts, checklists &amp; templates</strong>
              <span>Take them to meetings. Hand them to your contractor. Use them on day one.</span>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" fill="var(--gtw-blue)" />
              <path d="m8 12 3 3 5-6" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <strong>Live coaching with Roy — every Friday</strong>
              <span>Bring your bids, your contracts, your questions. Get answers on camera.</span>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" fill="var(--gtw-blue)" />
              <path d="m8 12 3 3 5-6" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <strong>Zero hidden agendas</strong>
              <span>Roy isn't selling you a service. He's selling you the truth. One price. That's it.</span>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .solution__layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.1fr;
    gap: 4.5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .solution__visual {
    position: relative;
  }
  .solution__visual-main {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }
  .solution__visual-main img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  .solution__visual-accent {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -2rem;
    right: -2.5rem;
    width: 55%;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    border: 8px solid var(--gtw-white);
  }
  .solution__visual-accent img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .solution__badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: 2rem;
    left: -2rem;
    background: var(--gtw-white);
    padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.8rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    max-width: 260px;
  }
  .solution__badge svg { color: var(--gtw-blue); flex-shrink: 0; }
  .solution__badge strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--gtw-dark);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .solution__badge span {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .solution__content h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--gtw-blue);
  }
  .solution__lead {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .solution__lead em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gtw-dark);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .solution__list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.1rem;
  }
  .solution__list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.9rem;
  }
  .solution__list svg { flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
  .solution__list strong {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gtw-dark);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
  .solution__list span {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.93rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1000px) {
    .solution__layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
    }
    .solution__visual {
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .solution__visual-accent {
      right: -1rem;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .solution__visual-accent { display: none; }
    .solution__badge {
      left: -0.25rem;
      max-width: 220px;
    }
  }
</style>
